    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cookie Match: Enhanced Edition  is now released on Google Play!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268310/extras/e8be31a3c3d109c2b69a6f9ff0feb724.avif?t=1700381943\" width=565 height=170 /></span><br><br><br>Cookie Match is a game that everyone can enjoy.<br>To match cookies and cookie cutters or icings, you will face different tricks in each room, that gives you a unique experience and entertainment. <br>Clear all the stages and reveal cookies' true stories!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to play</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Move cookies to place them in the matching cookie cutters or the matching cookie icings. <br></li><li>All the cookies move in the same direction as a set. <br></li><li>Once a cookie meets the matching cutter or the matching cookie icing, the decoration is completed.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Caution</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Butter packs are unmovable, like a wall.<br></li><li>If a cookie hits the cutlery or a pigeon, then the cookie is fallen apart.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Control the direction with arrow keys or WASD (up / left / down / right) or touch / swipe<br></li><li>R for the stage reset<br></li><li>F for fullscreen on / off<br></li><li>ESC for the previous page <br></li><li>Backspace or Delete key for undo<br></li><li>M for music on / off</li></ul><br>* Background music from Epidemic Sound",
